replies.author: luzhengwei
replies.txt_content:
本帖最后由 luzhengwei 于 2018-8-25 13:57 编辑 

https://github.com/PaperMC/Paper/issues/991 根据GameBox插件作者的描述，这个问题是mojang的一个bug不是spigot本身的原因.追根究源是由于mojang 网络API不稳定导致的，只能通过插件作者使用新的头颅API进行设置 并进行缓存。具体原因及方案由Paper作者描述如下：you will have to consult those plugins authors.This isn't a bug. Stuff is doing exactly as it's told to, and network issues happen.Before that change, trying to set named base skulls would not work on the first open until the profile was cached.So its best for plugin authors to cache the head on start, and even better would be to save it to a .yml file once looked up, but the best would be something like this:https://github.com/TigerHix/Hex-Utils/blob/master/hex/util/Skull.java#L70Set the texture payload directly on GameProfile (add authlib as a PROVIDED dependency to your plugin)当然以上都是给开发者的。
所以综上，先将这个问题反馈给插件作者，然后尝试更新最新的Spigot版本。
